'''蟹状星云脉冲星'''（PSR B0531+21）是一颗相当年轻的[[中子星|中子星]]。它是超新星[[SN_1054|SN 1054]]的[[超新星遗迹|遗迹]]——[[蟹状星云|蟹状星云]]中心的天体。那颗超新星当时在地球上的许多国家都有观测记录<ref name="SN1054">{{Cite web|title=Supernova 1054 - Creation of the Crab Nebula|url=http://www.messier.seds.org/more/m001_sn.html|accessdate=2021-04-28|work=www.messier.seds.org|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428122148/http://www.messier.seds.org/more/m001_sn.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Ancient Oriental Chronicles|url=http://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/125409|last=Duyvendak|first=J. J. L.|date=1942-04-XX|journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific|doi=10.1086/125409|volume=54|pages=91|language=en|issn=0004-6280|access-date=2021-04-28|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430150755/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/125409|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Astronomical Aspects|url=http://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/125410|last=Mayall|first=N. U.|last2=Oort|first2=J. H.|date=1942-04-XX|journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific|doi=10.1086/125410|volume=54|pages=95|language=en|issn=0004-6280|access-date=2021-04-28|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430044836/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1086/125410|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Ancient records and the Crab Nebula supernova|url=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1983Obs...103..106B/abstract|last=Brecher|first=K.|last2=Fesen|first2=R. A.|date=1983-06-XX|journal=The Observatory|volume=103|pages=106–113|language=en|issn=0029-7704|last3=Maran|first3=S. P.|last4=Brandt|first4=J. C.|access-date=2021-04-28|archive-date=2019-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190707034454/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1983Obs...103..106B|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该脉冲星于1968年发现，成为首颗已确认与[[超新星遗迹|超新星遗迹]]有关的脉冲星<ref>{{Cite book|edition=4th ed|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/38157539|publisher=Brooks/Cole, Cengage Learning|date=1998|location=Belmont Drive, CA|isbn=0-03-006228-4|oclc=38157539|first=Michael|last=Zeilik|title=Introductory astronomy & astrophysics|access-date=2021-04-28|archive-date=2020-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528211148/https://www.worldcat.org/title/introductory-astronomy-astrophysics/oclc/38157539|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
